{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01GRPEm9HXhwYrjRLbvopCvU","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a thorough understanding of the codebase. Let me analyze what needs to happen for this migration:\n\n**Current state:** Spring Boot + JoinFaces (JSF integration) application with:\n- Spring Boot starters (web, data-jpa, validation)\n- JoinFaces for JSF integration\n- Jakarta Faces (JSF 4.0) for the UI\n- JPA with H2 for persistence\n- WAR packaging\n\n**Target:** Pure Jakarta EE application (no Spring). This means:\n- Replace Spring Boot with a Jakarta EE runtime (e.g., embedded Tomcat/Jetty or a lightweight app server)\n- Replace Spring DI with Jakarta CDI\n- Replace Spring Data JPA with Jakarta Persistence (manual EntityManager)\n- Replace Spring annotations with Jakarta equivalents\n- The JSF parts already use `jakarta.faces` namespace, which is good\n\nLet me now plan the detailed migration approach and start implementing:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":9473,"cache_read_input_tokens":32183,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":9473,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":814},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5178e60b-6983-4b64-b8b8-e65cc691e770","uuid":"db574f05-84cf-4e3b-8dc5-3fb82c3c4278"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01GRPEm9HXhwYrjRLbvopCvU","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01RaY235W5RgDfzzEMcfPEfJ","name":"TodoWrite","input":{"todos":[{"content":"Read all source files to understand the complete codebase","status":"completed","activeForm":"Reading all source files"},{"content":"Design Jakarta EE architecture - replace Spring Boot with pure Jakarta EE","status":"in_progress","activeForm":"Designing Jakarta EE architecture"},{"content":"Rewrite pom.xml for Jakarta EE (CDI, JPA, Faces, Servlet)","status":"pending","activeForm":"Rewriting pom.xml for Jakarta EE"},{"content":"Create REST endpoints for smoke test coverage (health + CRUD API)","status":"pending","activeForm":"Creating REST endpoints"},{"content":"Refactor Application.java - remove Spring Boot, use CDI/Servlet","status":"pending","activeForm":"Refactoring Application.java"},{"content":"Refactor ContactController - Spring DI to CDI","status":"pending","activeForm":"Refactoring ContactController"},{"content":"Refactor ContactService - Spring @Service/@Transactional to CDI/JTA","status":"pending","activeForm":"Refactoring ContactService"},{"content":"Refactor ContactRepository - Spring Data JPA to Jakarta Persistence","status":"pending","activeForm":"Refactoring ContactRepository"},{"content":"Remove SpringConfig, ServletInitializer, JsfConfig - replace with Jakarta equivalents","status":"pending","activeForm":"Removing Spring config classes"},{"content":"Update application config (persistence.xml, web.xml, beans.xml)","status":"pending","activeForm":"Updating configuration files"},{"content":"Update Dockerfile for Jakarta EE build and run","status":"pending","activeForm":"Updating Dockerfile"},{"content":"Generate smoke tests (smoke.py)","status":"pending","activeForm":"Generating smoke tests"},{"content":"Build Docker image and verify application starts","status":"pending","activeForm":"Building Docker image"},{"content":"Run smoke tests against the container","status":"pending","activeForm":"Running smoke tests"},{"content":"Document all changes in CHANGELOG.md","status":"pending","activeForm":"Documenting changes in CHANGELOG.md"}]}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":9473,"cache_read_input_tokens":32183,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":9473,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":814},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5178e60b-6983-4b64-b8b8-e65cc691e770","uuid":"5580a3ea-8497-489e-8df7-ceac91a58d31"}
