ges (moved from resources)\n- src/main/webapp/resources/css/jsfcrud.css: Stylesheet (moved)\n- smoke.py: 11 smoke test cases\n- CHANGELOG.md: Full migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbookspring/ (entire old package)\n  - Application.java: Spring Boot main class\n  - ServletInitializer.java: SpringBootServletInitializer\n  - config/SpringConfig.java: @Configuration/@ComponentScan\n  - config/JsfConfig.java: FacesServlet @Bean registration\n  - repo/ContactRepository.java: Spring Data JPA repository\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Spring Boot config\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/resources/: Old JSF resources location\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/faces-config.xml: Old location\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n- **Error count:** 1 build error (Docker), resolved on attempt 2\n- **Error:** WildFly CentOS 7 base image lacked C++ compiler for greenlet (playwright dependency)\n- **Resolution:** Switched runtime base to Ubuntu 22.04 with manual WildFly installation\n- **No manual intervention required**"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":476,"cache_read_input_tokens":98286,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":476,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":859},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5178e60b-6983-4b64-b8b8-e65cc691e770","uuid":"2473aa20-38d2-4f4e-80f9-76d3300ce032"}
